2026-05-10T17:53:06.2507044Z 238        <!--
2026-05-10T17:53:06.2507434Z 239            Override Google Play Billing's ProxyBillingActivity so the system
2026-05-10T17:53:06.2507777Z 240            cannot restore it from Recents or after process death with a
2026-05-10T17:53:06.2508121Z 241            stale Intent. The library's onCreate reads the PendingIntent
2026-05-10T17:53:06.2508478Z 242            extra without null-checking; if Android recreates the activity
2026-05-10T17:53:06.2508709Z 243            and the extra is missing, it NPEs on
